it was like being hypnotized.

7
00:02:53,540 --> 00:02:56,270
I was 20years old.
It was the late '60s...

8
00:02:56,376 --> 00:02:59,436
and I'd come to Paris
for a year to study French.

9
00:02:59,546 --> 00:03:01,571
