84
00:07:37,123 --> 00:07:38,818
Whyis Carne here?

85
00:07:38,925 --> 00:07:42,156
What should we do?
Stay or leave?

86
00:07:42,261 --> 00:07:44,627
I don't know.

87
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:48,461
