I'm cooking for two...

180
00:15:09,675 --> 00:15:11,233
and now there are
five of us.

181
00:15:11,343 --> 00:15:12,435
Didn't Theo
tell you?

182
00:15:12,544 --> 00:15:15,274
No, he didn't.
And neither did you.

183
00:15:15,381 --> 00:15:18,544
